message: Added deletion vote. The entire article is filled with inaccurate information and cites unreliable and obsolete sources that are irrelevant to the content.

page: José Sarmiento de Valladares, 1st Duke of Atrisco
message: Deleted the last name “Arines-Troncoso de Romay” which was his sixth last name not second. José Sarmiento Valladares, 1st Duke of Atrisco, was the son of Gregorio Sarmiento de Valladares and Juana Sarmiento y Niño de Castro. He was the grandson of Luis Sarmiento de Valladares and Inés de Arines Troncoso y Romay. The duke did not adopt his sixth last name, which belonged to his great-grandmother.
